    <h2>About Chikankari</h2>
    <p>
      Chikankari is a traditional embroidery art that originated in Lucknow, Uttar Pradesh.
      It involves intricate hand embroidery on fabrics like cotton, georgette, and silk.
    </p>

    <h2>Our Products</h2>
    <h3>Kurtis</h3>
    <p>Elegant and lightweight kurtis for daily and festive wear.</p>

    <h3>Sarees</h3>
