    <h3>Men's Wear</h3>
    <p>Kurta pajama, shirts, trousers, and blazers with chikankari work.</p>

    <h2>Market Presence</h2>
    <h3>Lucknow</h3>
    <p>Main hub of chikankari. Price range: ₹500 - ₹5000</p>

    <h3>Delhi</h3>
    <p>High demand for designer wear. Price range: ₹1000 - ₹6000</p>

    <h3>Jaipur</h3>
